text: Baron Kingsdown may refer to: *Thomas Pemberton Leigh, 1st Baron Kingsdown (1793-1867), British politician. *Robin Leigh-Pemberton, Baron Kingsdown (1927-2013), British lawyer and banker, kinsman of the above.
